quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,1,"Most blessed is He Who sent down this Criterion on His servant, to be a warner to all mankind;",footnotes:179602:1,footnotes:179603:2,footnotes:179604:3,footnotes:179605:4
  25,2,"He to Whom belongs the kingdom of the heavens and the earth; Who has taken to Himself no son nor has He taken any partner in His kingdom; Who created everything and then determined its destiny.",footnotes:179606:1,footnotes:179607:2,footnotes:179608:3,footnotes:179609:4